nodes.text: Wynne Organa was a Human male from House Organa, serving as Chief negotiator of the peace talks in order to end the civil war on Alderaan.

In 3643 BBY, Wynne met with Jedi Master Orgus Din and his apprentice. He informed them that Aleyna Hark never made it to her cell, and she had been missing for hours. Discovering that she was a spy to the Sith Empire, she had been spotted recently entering a compound of House Thul in the Juran Mountains.
